Sql_wrapper is a c++ template oriented wrapper for sqlite.

Features
- A user friendly API
- Execute queries, write/read data from/to common conainers.
- Easy to extend to custom data types, and custom containers
- A way to execute a function in parallel for each line of obtained data

More details, and complete documentation is available online here
https://tentacule.be/fossil/cpp-sql_wrapper/index

